OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fmostly dry and mild overnight with
OL,7,Fvariable amounts of cloud and some
OL,8,Fclearer spells. Chance of patchy light
OL,9,Frain mainly across north-western parts
OL,10,Flater on in the night. Winds
OL,11,Ffreshening a little.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAny patchy rain or showers
OL,14,Fclearing southeast by late morning.
OL,15,FBecoming fine with some bright and
OL,16,Fsunny spells by the afternoon but
OL,17,Fbecoming a little breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
